  "excerpt": "<p>4 Steps to getting health insurance under the ACA. Find out how, when to get health coverage and if you qualify for savings. Preview plans &amp; pricing.</p>",
  "content": "<div data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"e7943b48-db95-4ad9-9d3e-1d8fb3dfb4ac\" data-embed-button=\"brief\" data-entity-embed-display=\"view_mode:node.inline\" data-langcode=\"en\" data-entity-embed-display-settings=\"[]\" class=\"embedded-entity\">\n<article class=\"node node--type-brief node--view-mode-inline\">\n\n  \n    \n\n  \n  <div class=\"node__content\">\n    \n            <div class=\"clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-content-body field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field__item\"><div class=\"box-content information-heavyweight\"><div class=\"content\"><strong>Get health coverage now if you qualify for:</strong></div><ul><li><div class=\"content\">A <a class=\"ck ck-tooltip\" href=\"/node/39946\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"4efe1a01-b960-4b16-9053-0fe27a180a34\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"39946\" data-entity-bundle=\"brief\" title=\"Special Enrollment Period (term tooltip)\">Special Enrollment Period</a> due to a life event, like moving, losing other coverage, getting married, or having a baby.</div></li><li><div class=\"content\">Free or low-cost coverage through <a href=\"/glossary/medicaid\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"13c0081d-9e96-420a-a724-6e81e89d20c1\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"35311\" data-entity-bundle=\"glossary\" title=\"Medicaid\">Medicaid</a> or the <a href=\"/glossary/childrens-health-insurance-program-chip\" data-link-button-type=\"1\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"87f4b3ac-b0c4-45b7-a691-d5b2cc35aac3\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"35631\" data-entity-bundle=\"glossary\" title=\"Children's Health Insurance Program (CHIP)\">Children's Health Insurance Program (CHIP)</a>.</div></li></ul><div class=\"content\"><a href=\"/screener/\" data-link-button-type=\"1\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"2fe96e5a-1008-4641-a0ea-08c4df5081d6\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"40021\" data-entity-bundle=\"link\" title=\"SEP screener\">Check if you qualify.</a></div></div></div>\n      \n  </div>\n\n</article>\n</div>\n<p>If you\u2019re new to the <a href=\"/glossary/health-insurance-marketplace-glossary\" title=\"Health Insurance Marketplace\u00ae\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"ed1006f1-9189-41ae-ae28-6c20ec496af5\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-content=\"A service that helps people shop for and enroll in health insurance. The federal government operates the Health Insurance Marketplace\u00ae, available at HealthCare.gov, for most states. Some states run their own Marketplaces.\" data-entity-bundle=\"glossary\" data-entity-id=\"35431\" data-internal-href=\"/node/35431\" data-original-title=\"Health Insurance Marketplace\u00ae\">Marketplace</a>, follow these 4 steps to apply and enroll.</p><p>Already have an account?&nbsp;<a href=\"/login\">Log in to apply.</a></p><div class=\"ds-l-container ds-u-padding-x--2\"><div class=\"ds-l-row ds-u-border--2 ds-u-padding--2 ds-u-margin-y--2\"><div class=\"ds-l-md-col--1 ds-u-md-display--block ds-u-display--none\">&nbsp;</div><div class=\"ds-l-col--12 ds-l-sm-col--10 ds-l-md-col--8\"><p class=\"ds-u-margin-top--0\"><strong>Before you get started: Get key resources</strong></p><ul style=\"padding-inline-start:20px;\"><li><a href=\"/coverage/what-marketplace-plans-cover\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"15f5701d-728d-4893-b2b6-c27a19b51ce4\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37336\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"What Marketplace health insurance plans cover\">Discover what Marketplace plans cover</a>, including treatment for pre-existing medical conditions and other essential health benefits.</li><li><a href=\"/see-plans\">Preview health plans and prices to get an estimate.</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"ds-u-md-display--block ds-u-display--none ds-l-md-col--3 ds-u-padding-left--4 ds-u-text-align--center\"><img alt=\"icon: three books\" src=\"https://www.healthcare.gov/assets/roadmap-icon-key-resources.svg\"></div></div><div class=\"ds-l-row ds-u-border--2 ds-u-padding--2 ds-u-margin-y--2\"><div class=\"ds-l-col--2 ds-l-md-col--1\"><span class=\"ds-u-color--white ds-u-display--block ds-u-fill--base ds-u-font-size--xl ds-u-margin-x--auto ds-u-radius--circle ds-u-text-align--center\" style=\"height:32px;width:32px;\">1</span></div><div class=\"ds-l-col--10 ds-l-md-col--8\"><p class=\"ds-u-margin-top--0\"><strong>Create a Marketplace account</strong></p><ul style=\"padding-inline-start:20px;\"><li>Enter some basic information, like your name, address, and email address to start.</li><li>If your state <a href=\"/marketplace-in-your-state\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"7eadbde2-3ffe-45f5-bc14-ee18670a8a12\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36131\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"The Marketplace in your state\">runs its own Marketplace</a>, we\u2019ll take you there.</li></ul><p><a class=\"ds-c-button ds-c-button--solid\" href=\"/create-account\">Create account</a></p></div><div class=\"ds-u-md-display--block ds-u-display--none ds-l-md-col--3 ds-u-padding-left--4 ds-u-text-align--center\"><img alt=\"icon: silhouette of a person with a check mark in front\" src=\"https://www.healthcare.gov/assets/roadmap-icon-create-account.svg\"></div></div><div class=\"ds-l-row ds-u-border--2 ds-u-padding--2 ds-u-margin-y--2\"><div class=\"ds-l-col--2 ds-l-md-col--1\"><span class=\"ds-u-color--white ds-u-display--block ds-u-fill--base ds-u-font-size--xl ds-u-margin-x--auto ds-u-radius--circle ds-u-text-align--center\" style=\"height:32px;width:32px;\">2</span></div><div class=\"ds-l-col--10 ds-l-md-col--8\"><p class=\"ds-u-margin-top--0\"><strong>Get ready to apply</strong></p><ul style=\"padding-inline-start:20px;\"><li><a href=\"/apply-and-enroll/get-ready-to-apply\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"2de853d2-9492-4aa3-9bbf-ae91ad3a029d\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37261\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Get ready to apply for health coverage\">Learn how to get ready.</a></li><li><a href=\"/downloads/apply-for-or-renew-coverage.pdf\" data-entity-type=\"media\" data-entity-uuid=\"080994e2-ab56-43ad-9168-da794027a262\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"10906\" data-entity-bundle=\"document\" title=\"apply-for-or-renew-coverage.pdf\">Use this checklist to gather everything you may need</a> (PDF, 251 KB).</li><li><a href=\"/income-and-household-information\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"3120874d-3793-4b6e-93a6-c2a51506a8b3\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37596\" data-entity-bundle=\"explainer\" title=\"Count income &amp; household size\">Find out how to estimate your income</a> for your application.</li><li>Need help with your application? <a href=\"/apply-and-enroll/how-to-apply\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"5288731d-b82d-4a08-9da1-d02c5d3bcee4\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37276\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Ways to apply for health insurance\">Learn ways to apply for health coverage.</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"ds-u-md-display--block ds-u-display--none ds-l-md-col--3 ds-u-padding-left--4 ds-u-text-align--center\"><img alt=\"icon: papers with a pencil\" src=\"https://www.healthcare.gov/assets/roadmap-icon-get-ready.svg\"></div></div><div class=\"ds-l-row ds-u-border--2 ds-u-padding--2 ds-u-margin-y--2\"><div class=\"ds-l-col--2 ds-l-md-col--1\"><span class=\"ds-u-color--white ds-u-display--block ds-u-fill--base ds-u-font-size--xl ds-u-margin-x--auto ds-u-radius--circle ds-u-text-align--center\" style=\"height:32px;width:32px;\">3</span></div><div class=\"ds-l-col--10 ds-l-md-col--8\"><p class=\"ds-u-margin-top--0\"><strong>Get \u201cEligibility Results\u201d right away</strong></p><p>Submit your application to find out if you qualify for:</p><ul style=\"padding-inline-start:20px;\"><li>A Marketplace health insurance plan with savings, like the <a href=\"/glossary/premium-tax-credit\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"d42500cd-967f-429f-81da-ee3e7bc40130\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"34736\" data-entity-bundle=\"glossary\" title=\"Premium tax credit\">premium tax credit</a> to help pay monthly <a href=\"/glossary/premium\" title=\"Premium\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"b625d61d-da5b-4825-bb54-2bb728b7a4c0\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-content=\"The amount you pay for your health insurance every month. In addition to your premium, you usually have to pay other costs for your health care, including a deductible, copayments, and coinsurance. If you have a Marketplace health plan, you may be able to lower your costs with a premium tax credit.\" data-entity-bundle=\"glossary\" data-entity-id=\"35151\" data-internal-href=\"/node/35151\" data-original-title=\"Premium\">premiums</a>, or lower <a href=\"/glossary/co-payment\" title=\"Copayment\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"8923e304-18ed-4cf7-bb09-9cfa370d6b5c\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-content=\"A fixed amount ($20, for example) you pay for a covered health care service after you've paid your deductible.\" data-entity-bundle=\"glossary\" data-entity-id=\"35611\" data-internal-href=\"/node/35611\" data-original-title=\"Copayment\">copayments</a>, <a href=\"/glossary/co-insurance\" title=\"Coinsurance\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"f12676c2-6d8f-4880-a942-74a098a3d582\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-content=\"The percentage of costs of a covered health care service you pay (20%, for example) after you've paid your deductible.\" data-entity-bundle=\"glossary\" data-entity-id=\"35616\" data-internal-href=\"/node/35616\" data-original-title=\"Coinsurance\">coinsurance</a>, and <a href=\"/glossary/deductible\" title=\"Deductible\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"fcb2fa69-9a31-41eb-a26a-5c76637d7625\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-content=\"The amount you pay for covered health care services before your insurance plan starts to pay. With a $2,000 deductible, for example, you pay the first $2,000 of covered services yourself.\" data-entity-bundle=\"glossary\" data-entity-id=\"34906\" data-internal-href=\"/node/34906\" data-original-title=\"Deductible\">deductibles</a>.</li><li><a href=\"/medicaid-chip/getting-medicaid-chip\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"845b29f0-0682-4d2d-ab42-9c013b3ec2e3\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37806\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Medicaid &amp; CHIP coverage\">Free or low-cost coverage through Medicaid and the Children\u2019s Health Insurance Program (CHIP).</a></li><li>Lower costs \u2014 <a href=\"/lower-costs/qualifying-for-lower-costs\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"19ae9afb-dba8-4f26-8db6-0977f0603208\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"38066\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Income levels &amp; savings\">See if you might save before you apply.</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"ds-u-md-display--block ds-u-display--none ds-l-md-col--3 ds-u-padding-left--4 ds-u-text-align--center\"><img alt=\"icon: computer screen with a check mark on it\" src=\"https://www.healthcare.gov/assets/roadmap-icon-get-results.svg\"></div></div><div class=\"ds-l-row ds-u-border--2 ds-u-padding--2 ds-u-margin-y--2\"><div class=\"ds-l-col--2 ds-l-md-col--1\"><span class=\"ds-u-color--white ds-u-display--block ds-u-fill--base ds-u-font-size--xl ds-u-margin-x--auto ds-u-radius--circle ds-u-text-align--center\" style=\"height:32px;width:32px;\">4</span></div><div class=\"ds-l-col--10 ds-l-md-col--7\"><p class=\"ds-u-margin-top--0\"><strong>Enroll in health coverage</strong></p><ul style=\"padding-inline-start:20px;\"><li>Compare health plans and prices available in your area, and enroll in the one that best meets your needs.</li><li><a href=\"/choose-a-plan/comparing-plans\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"a61e08a4-076c-4f97-bf42-5412cffcd8cd\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37841\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"3 things to know before you pick a health insurance plan\">Learn how to pick a plan.</a> <span>Or, watch the video.</span></li><li>Need dental coverage too? <a href=\"/coverage/dental-coverage\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"69ec39b1-5ba6-4e36-a47e-c371940888b8\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37316\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Dental coverage in the Marketplace\">Discover 2 ways to get it.</a></li><li><a href=\"/apply-and-enroll/complete-your-enrollment\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"65636127-2a63-4f89-ac7e-004b529a7a23\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37251\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Complete your enrollment &amp; pay your first premium\">Pay your premium</a> to your insurance company for your coverage to start.</li><li>Ready to apply &amp; enroll? <a href=\"/login\">Log in</a>.</li></ul></div><div class=\"ds-l-col--12 ds-l-md-col--4 ds-u-padding-left--4\"><div class=\"media-modal\" data-modal-heading=\"How to Choose a Plan in the Health Insurance Marketplace\u00ae\"><div class=\"media-modal-trigger\"><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default\" data-align=\"center\">\n  \n      \n  <div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\">\n    <div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div>\n              <div class=\"field__item\">    <img loading=\"eager\" data-image-encoded=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-image-width=\"220\" data-image-height=\"132\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_small_544/public/inline-images/en/how-to-choose-a-plan-in-the-health-insurance-marketplace.jpeg?itok=lUAgaOpf 544w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_medium_768/public/inline-images/en/how-to-choose-a-plan-in-the-health-insurance-marketplace.jpeg?itok=5clPGuod 768w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/en/how-to-choose-a-plan-in-the-health-insurance-marketplace.jpeg?itok=99K5OHo1 1024w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1290px) 1290px, 100vw\" width=\"1024\" height=\"614\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/en/how-to-choose-a-plan-in-the-health-insurance-marketplace.jpeg?itok=99K5OHo1\" alt=\"How to choose a plan in the health insurance marketplace\" title=\"How to choose a plan in the health insurance marketplace\">\n\n\n</div>\n          </div>\n\n            <div class=\"field field--name-field-spanish-image field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image-es media--view-mode-default\">\n  \n      \n            <div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image-spanish field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\">    <img loading=\"eager\" data-image-encoded=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-image-width=\"220\" data-image-height=\"132\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_small_544/public/inline-images/es/how-to-choose-a-plan-in-the-health-insurance-marketplace.jpeg?itok=KyAfyvqQ 544w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_medium_768/public/inline-images/es/how-to-choose-a-plan-in-the-health-insurance-marketplace.jpeg?itok=UOgQDlxE 768w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/es/how-to-choose-a-plan-in-the-health-insurance-marketplace.jpeg?itok=fqCXxAPS 1024w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1290px) 1290px, 100vw\" width=\"1024\" height=\"614\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/es/how-to-choose-a-plan-in-the-health-insurance-marketplace.jpeg?itok=fqCXxAPS\" alt>\n\n\n</div>\n      \n  </article>\n</div>\n      \n  </article>\n</div><div class=\"media-modal-content\"><div class=\"yt-iframe\" data-iframe-height=\"400\" data-iframe-src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/E45xOGIcGWo?wmode=transparent&amp;rel=0&amp;enablejsapi=1\" data-iframe-width=\"100%\" title=\"YouTube Embedded Video: The Marketplace for Individuals and Families\">&nbsp;</div></div></div><p class=\"ds-u-margin--0\">How to Choose a Plan in the Health Insurance Marketplace\u00ae</p></div></div></div><h2>After you enroll</h2><ul><li>You\u2019ll get a packet in the mail with your new insurance card and more information about your health plan.&nbsp;<a href=\"/using-marketplace-coverage\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"00b2b908-5bd1-4a43-9d3c-01827e82b50e\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37151\" data-entity-bundle=\"explainer\" title=\"Using your health insurance coverage\">Start using your coverage.</a></li><li>If you need to&nbsp;<a href=\"/reporting-changes/how-to-report-changes\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"1fc76093-b6e3-4264-beb9-0c66e430c157\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37436\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How to report changes to the Marketplace\">make changes to your plan</a>, you can do so if you're moving, having a baby, or adopting a child.</li><li>If your income or household changes, update your application as soon as possible. Your coverage options and savings may be impacted.</li><li>If you\u2019re eligible for Medicaid or CHIP, you\u2019ll get information and next steps from your state.</li></ul>",
  "url": "/quick-guide/getting-marketplace-health-insurance"
}